embeds.description:
Discord **Requires** Message Content Intents to be enabled, for bots to read guild messages. You can enable the privileged intent by going to your bot application's page on the [Discord Developer Portal](https://discord.com/developers), then navigating to `Bot > Privileged Gateway Intents` and enabling `Message Content Intent`. Restart your server, and EssentialsX will be able to read messages from your guild. 

For more information, see [this message](https://ptb.discord.com/channels/390942438061113344/426460619277991936/1015033747185356810)
embeds.title: Message Content Intent
